OL,3,CParents pay tribute to 'caring' boys
OL,4,Cwho died of injuries sustained in A30
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe parents of two boys who died
OL,8,Ffollowing a crash on the A30 in
OL,9,FCornwall have paid tribute to them.
OL,11,FTobias and Finley Rice were from the
OL,12,FChristchurch area of Dorset and were
OL,13,Ftravelling to St Ives when their car
OL,14,Fwas involved in a collision near
OL,15,FConnor Downs, on Friday 29 May.
OL,17,FEight-year-old Tobias died at the
OL,18,Fscene and his five-year-old brother
OL,19,FFinlay was taken to Bristol Children's
OL,20,FHospital, where he died of his
OL,21,Finjuries on Tuesday 2 June.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
