OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781118693
OL,3,CParents pay tribute to 'caring' boys
OL,4,Cwho died of injuries sustained in A30
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FSimon Croutear said: "Our whole school
OL,8,Fcommunity has been shocked and grieved
OL,9,Fby the tragic loss of Tobias and
OL,10,FFinley.
OL,12,F"They were cherished members of our
OL,13,Fschool family and will be immensely
OL,14,Fmissed. Our thoughts and prayers are
OL,15,Fwith their family who we are in touch
OL,16,Fwith and are supporting in every way
OL,17,Fwe can.
OL,19,F"We have also been ensuring that
OL,20,Fsupport is in place for other pupils,
OL,21,Fas well as staff, at the school."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
