PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781118693
OL,3,CParents pay tribute to 'caring' boys
OL,4,Cwho died of injuries sustained in A30
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FDetective inspector Andy Heath of
OL,8,FDevon and Cornwall Police serious
OL,9,Fcollisions investigation team said: "I
OL,10,Fthank those who have come forward to
OL,11,Fassist us following our appeals for
OL,12,Fwitnesses.
OL,14,F"We are continuing our investigation
OL,15,Finto the tragic deaths of Tobias and
OL,16,FFinley, and anyone with information
OL,17,Fwho has not contacted the police
OL,18,Falready should call 101, providing
OL,19,Freference 50260136471.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781118693
OL,3,CParents pay tribute to 'caring' boys
OL,4,Cwho died of injuries sustained in A30
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"Specially trained officers continue
OL,8,Fto support the family and further
OL,9,Finformation will be released at the
OL,10,Fappropriate time."
OL,12,FA local man in his 60s was arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving and causing serious
OL,15,Finjury by dangerous driving. He was
OL,16,Ftreated for minor injuries.
